      "span_text": "In biomethane potential (BMP) assay we used biomass of common wetland plants: reed canary grass (Phalaris arundinacea L.), common reed (Phragmites australis (Cav.) Trin. ex Steud), reed sweet-grass (Glyceria maxima (Hartm.) Holmb.), tufted sedge (Carex elata All.) and woollyfruit sedge (Carex lasiocarpa Ehrh.)  .",
